THIRD PARTY LICENSES
====================

This project includes and builds upon the following open source software:

demo-magic.sh
-------------
Copyright (c) 2017 Paxton Hare
Licensed under the MIT License
Source: https://github.com/paxtonhare/demo-magic

The demo-magic.sh script (located in src/demo-magic.sh) is used for creating
interactive terminal demonstrations with simulated typing effects.

asciinema
---------
Used for recording terminal sessions
Source: https://asciinema.org/
Licensed under the GNU General Public License v3.0

